title.narrative: Enhanced local capacity to develop and operationalise IECD centered, equitable and inclusive high impact child survival anddevelopment packages in focus provinces

description.narrative: The three provinces supported by UNICEF enhanced their capacity to implement the IECD programme. Packages on essential specific nutrition interventions for pregnant women and children under 5, the package on early essential newborn care, and the communal IECD clubs were formulated, while its operational implementation was demonstrated. Experiences from IECD in pilot provinces have been used for policy advocacy at the national level and these packages have the potential to be scaled up nationwide. | Status:Partially met | As-of Date:03/02/2022
